  "body": "**Description**\r\nAccording to Discord user:\r\nnflaig \r\nHey, I've been using Nethermind as RPC with Metamask for a while now but I noticed on few occasions that the eth_estimateGas API returns incorrect gas limits causing txs to run out of gas (e.g. https://etherscan.io/tx/0x4ce8bf18b702ad810bded432b4f59b20ee038b6828fb45e633cc199c944c2fce).\r\n\r\nI created a gist (https://gist.github.com/nflaig/ea5b1b3f0413cd36e4391cad110ec177) to reproduce this for the failed tx I reported above.\r\n\r\nWe should not throw out of gas for sure (we can have different estimation than others but we should estimate enough value of gas for sure)",
